Name: vidcutter
Version: 3.0.0
Summary: the simple & fast video cutter & joiner with the help of mpv + FFmpeg
Home-page: http://vidcutter.ozmartians.com
Author: Pete Alexandrou
Author-email: pete@ozmartians.com
